# Movie Finder — Cursor Rules

## Project
Internal tool for finding and browsing movies.

## Stack
- Next.js 15 (App Router)
- TypeScript (strict)
- Tailwind CSS
- Deployed on Vercel

## Conventions
- All components in `src/components/`, co-located with their styles if needed
- Server components by default; add `"use client"` only when necessary
- Fetch data in Server Components or Route Handlers, not in client components
- Use TypeScript interfaces for all data shapes
- Prefer `async/await` over `.then()` chains
- Keep components small and single-purpose
